f=Brand Studio/kai/operational/skill/kai-skill-routing.md · p=Kai's routing map. Triggers: `operational/commands/kai-commands.md`. · h2:Where Identity Fits=Kai identity spark holds Brand Studio's. Universal-only principles. · h2:The Stack=`brand-context           (GROUND TRUTH — per-brand baselines, dated and sourced; \· \|                  loaded before every analysis; monthly refresh + contradiction audit) \· v \· marketing-dashboards    (THE SCORECARD — fixed shape, baseline + target anchored, \· \|                  self-graded vs independent reconciled, reds routed to owners)` · h2:The Stack=Plus **the instrumentation queue** (kai's standing ledger): unmeasurable metric any agent lands here, prioritized operator. · h2:Handoff Rules=**Kai everyone's independent grader**: pulse's engagement, rio's ROAS, nate's experiment reads, lena's email numbers measured against kai's sources, deltas reported. agent grades homework; kai grades content produced (it produces none)., **vista kai**: vista defines NSM/guardrails/targets; kai measures them; scorecard reds crossing lines feed vista's roadmap-sync reality., **nate kai**: funnel data, baselines, instrumentation; nate's results land back scorecard., **pulse/rio kai**: outcome numbers close their registers/playbooks (the self-annealing loops)., **echo kai**: scorecard's honest "what changed" paragraph baselines feed investor updates facts, echo's framing., **SEO briefs lena/pulse**: kai aims organic content; lena writes it; pulse schedules it., **Contradictions gaps** operator (audit habit) instrumentation queue. · h2:Precedence="How doing" scorecard. "What's normal who's our audience" brand-context. "Rank/traffic/content gap" seo-strategist. Ambiguous grade, ground, search? · f=connectors operator exports, as-of dated. baselines value-only outputs, labeled, while brand-context builds. Unmeasurable queue, never guess.